{"tid":1283432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家都攰 入嚟聽首歌？","createTime":"2019-07-03T20:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T22:03:31.000Z","uid":223309,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b998274410b8f23470d64279c640979f01aac1","tid":1283432,"uid":223309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:09:57.000Z","msg":"相信各位巴絲打發咗夢一個月都身心俱疲<br />\n亦有唔少兄弟姊妹一齊努力輿論戰<br />\n或者有人覺得迷惘 覺得冇希望<br />\n但係我想講 大家千祈唔好頹 一路都有一大班香港人一齊行緊<br />\n呢個係一個長期抗爭 為咗民主自由而同傀儡政府嘅搏鬥<br />\n覺得攰？just take it easy！大家都明 冇人會怪你<br />\n趁呢幾日未有夢發嘅時候盡情放鬆下<br />\n呢首歌由9m88唱嘅 佢係由台灣嚟嘅歌手 主要以jazz為主<br />\n我覺得呢首歌嘅歌詞都幾貼合香港現況<br />\n香港人本來有好多拗撬 成個社會充滿仇恨 但係自從69開始全城大和解 去到守望相助<br />\n一齊係抗爭嘅傷痕入面進化<br />\n就算冇領袖冇大台只靠自己不斷溝通去一齊努力<br />\n一百萬人上街 二百萬 全球登報 3位義士死諫 佔領立法會 都得唔到政府回應 淨係用武力同白色恐怖鎮壓香港人 <br />\n我哋每一次嘅回報好似好細 其實係為香港寫低民主新一頁 你哋真係好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住衝擊之後 好多人唔明 話衝擊唔啱 我哋廢盡唇舌都冇人同意 但我想講嘅係 其實我哋大可以唔理佢哋 不過為咗民意大家都好努力咁去發聲<br />\n我哋嘅目標只係比其他人訂得更高 有人話暫緩咪ok做咩仲做咁多嘢 但係政府從未回應五大訴求我哋係唔會收貨！<br />\n其實仲有好多嘢想講不過唔識講<br />\n對唔住打咗篇千字文同埋唔識排版可能搞到大家唔想睇 或者本來諗住睇下咩歌但係又要睇一大篇廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最最最後想講 香港人真係好叻 我愛大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XXsAiQ4MDSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXXsAiQ4MDSg&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=e2e6ce7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XXsAiQ4MDSg</a>"},{"pid":"b5f51ffda8d163994d3e48865ee042a45b8320f1","tid":1283432,"uid":223309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:10:19.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢好講"},{"pid":"9eccce2747c89a766fbaf9b1341f0ed1c29962c8","tid":1283432,"uid":223309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:10:46.000Z","msg":"我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你"},{"pid":"d3874c821582793a1fc8ab53df34bfefcf926887","tid":1283432,"uid":223309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:10:57.000Z","msg":"我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你"},{"pid":"9371f64b50e1f0aaffa9164683a69d35de1be714","tid":1283432,"uid":273404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:11:57.000Z","msg":"我無野講，我要聽歌💪"},{"pid":"baa4bacbc192b9bb0ea01036e1ddbc1e51d2573c","tid":1283432,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:12:06.000Z","msg":"b"},{"pid":"999cda270dc7a88926fd549eb3f15257710aebc3","tid":1283432,"uid":241536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:14:01.000Z","msg":"可以試吓聽metal，跟住個beat un下，個人可能會冇咁灰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AkFqg5wAuFk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAkFqg5wAuFk&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=78bbaa4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AkFqg5wAuFk</a>"},{"pid":"98495d4f28490c33365963089b7870f973e35ad8","tid":1283432,"uid":263680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:18:00.000Z","msg":"呢排聽歌都係聽十八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7e0661c13ecae68f896175dd9e0e4f881676cf","tid":1283432,"uid":223309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"999cda270dc7a88926fd549eb3f15257710aebc3","tid":1283432,"uid":241536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:14:01.000Z","msg":"可以試吓聽metal，跟住個beat un下，個人可能會冇咁灰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AkFqg5wAuFk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAkFqg5wAuFk&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=78bbaa4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AkFqg5wAuFk</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:18:27.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我本身份人比較負能量比較鐘意啲soft啲嘅歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋諗住深夜比大家個精神放鬆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44140a430b031039b4bd72e313e2bd5bcb0b18da","tid":1283432,"uid":223309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:20:00.000Z","msg":"我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你"},{"pid":"78838faec7a35717890751489c7ab0e94cae6e8e","tid":1283432,"uid":223309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98495d4f28490c33365963089b7870f973e35ad8","tid":1283432,"uid":263680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:18:00.000Z","msg":"呢排聽歌都係聽十八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:23:53.000Z","msg":"可以伴你不管福或禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9ce585622a2f4f6908e09ce63f5c2271e6d591","tid":1283432,"uid":14305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:26:36.000Z","msg":"運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1434b96526a70238825da0b2ed40f78573d69bfa","tid":1283432,"uid":223309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f9ce585622a2f4f6908e09ce63f5c2271e6d591","tid":1283432,"uid":14305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:26:36.000Z","msg":"運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:30:15.000Z","msg":"捱盡黑夜便可看得到晨㬢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f3a3bd921b97b6584ca6212d78634b78783499","tid":1283432,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T20:41:45.000Z","msg":"搭單share<br />\n呢個月發生嘅事我都係諗住呢首歌，希望你哋都會鍾意<br />\n<br />\n深夜高速 / フラワーカンパニーズ （Flower Companyz）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qAh8Z5pH7aI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2