.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我無嘢講<br />\n<br />\n大家撐住加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7ec001beff29741284fab221c4907d73584a66","tid":1283432,"uid":271456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8409ce287727bf18876f37f4c9006c47b32ddd4a","tid":1283432,"uid":271456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T21:37:57.000Z","msg":"除了那首Can you hear my heart 之外，還有首大陸的一首歌 - 齊天 華晨宇<br />\n<br />\n歌詞也很不錯，也有些像現在的我們的情況，<br />\n<br />\n什麼人命天定我說天命由心<br />\n我要這山斷不了來路<br />\n我要這水擋不住歸途<br />\n我要天地都為我讓步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aJMTduUTX8Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaJMTduUTX8Y&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=bc071422\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aJMTduUTX8Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0VbVHb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0VbVHb.png&h=a6f81f75&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T22:03:31.000Z","msg":"首歌將孫悟空的無奈 怒吼 無能為力 演唱出來，<br />\n正如我們現在的香港年輕人一樣，我們充滿著無奈，怒吼的不滿，但我們又無能為力。"}]}